{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be minimalist and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard - Cybersecurity Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #007bff;\n            --secondary-color: #e0f2ff;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: var(--primary-color) 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n        }\n\n        .services {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        .services h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>SecureGuard</h1>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Your Digital Fortress</h2>\n            <p>Protecting your business from evolving cyber threats with cutting-edge security solutions. We provide comprehensive services to ensure your data and systems remain safe and resilient.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"row\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Risk Assessment</h4>\n                    <p>Identify vulnerabilities and assess potential threats to your digital assets.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n                    <h4>Threat Detection & Response</h4>\n                    <p>Proactive monitoring and rapid response to neutralize security incidents